val.value: Cinematic - a blast of raw magical energy erupts from Shadowheart, overcoming the Sister Superior. Then darkness. Shadowheart comes to in a torture chair, much like the one the others were in previously. She’s clearly been through a lot. Another Sharran tortures her with a strange thin dagger.
Shadowheart is alone in her torture chair after a long seven weeks. The Mother Superior comes to her.
The Sister Superior gestures to a selection of torture implements near the two captives.

Shadowheart transitions from one torture chamber to another. Another time and place - the cloister. Her clothing is different. And she is not alone. She seated seated before two bound prisoners - a human man and a half-elf woman. To her side is a an array of torture implements, much like the room we were just in. Another figure stands behind her, watching and instructing. The Sister Superior.

Shadowheart transitions from one torture chamber to another, along with the party. Another time and place - the cloister. Her clothing is different. And she is not alone. She seated seated before two bound prisoners - a human man and a half-elf woman. To her side is a an array of torture implements, much like the room we were just in. Another figure stands behind her, watching and instructing. The Sister Superior.
The strange magical glow from before returns. Stronger than before.
Sister Superior notices the magic glow, reacts to it.

Cinematic - a blast of raw magical energy erupts from Shadowheart, overcoming the Sister Superior. Then darkness. Shadowheart comes to in a torture chair, much like the one the others were in previously. She’s clearly been through a lot. Another Sharran tortures her with a strange thin dagger.

The Sharran torturer uses the strange dagger to inflict great agony on Shadowheart, all centred on just one point of her arm. The scene fades down as time progresses. When it returns, seven weeks of this will have passed.

synopsis.value:
TEST DIALOGUE. Intended to represent the Shadowheart Gauntlet of Shar flashback OM. Placeholder Speakers:
High Priestess Reyna = Shar Sister Superior
Base Female Elf = Female captive of the Cloister (SH's mother)
Base Male Human = Male captive of the Cloister (SH's father)
Torturer Spike = Shadowheart's Shar Torturer
Minathara = Mother Superior of the Cloister
